text: Wiesław Kilian (25 July 1952 – 15 March 2019) was a Polish politician. He was elected to Sejm on 25 September 2005 getting 7,524 votes in Wrocław. He was a member of the Law and Justice. He joined Poland Comes First when that party split from Law and Justice in 2010. He was re-elected to the Sejm in 2010 and served until his death. Kilian died on 15 March 2019 in Warsaw from cardiac arrest, aged 66.Zmarł Wiesław Kilian, senator VIII i IX kadencji ==References== ==Other websites== *Wiesław Kilian - parliamentary page - includes declarations of interest, voting record, and transcripts of speeches.
